data.description: Attention first time home buyers and savvy investors! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity in Jonesboro! This charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath home is perfect for those looking to enter the real estate market or expand their portfolio. Enjoy the privacy of a fenced backyard and the convenience of a shop on the property. With its prime location, this property offers great potential for growth. Don't wait, seize this investment opportunity today! Call or text now to schedule a showing of 3010 Race St.
